Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:30.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,娜丁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nadine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德  我是过来跟你说点事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed, I've come to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你的车呢  你怎么过来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Honey, where's your car? How'd you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我走过来的  -你走来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I walked. - You walked?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,你拿着铲子干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's with the shovel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正想跟你说这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's what I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It is? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:44.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德  我来是想告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed, I've come to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  艾德  你知道我很爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, and Ed, you know I love you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  娜丁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you do, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:59.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我这么多年来一直对你很糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I've been a selfish bitch to you all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,而你一直都是个圣人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you've been a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:08.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道你爱诺玛她也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've known since forever you love Norma and she loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的嫉妒让你们分离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I kept the two of you apart because of my jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我操纵了你  艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I manipulated you, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不  你没有  娜丁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, you haven't, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你知道这是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, you know it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我让你觉得愧疚而留在我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guilted you to stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,而你太好了  真的留了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you're so good you stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,放弃了自己的爱情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and gave up your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, god, Ed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你问拿这把铲子怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You asked about this shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:40.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正把自己从屎里铲出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm shoveling myself out of the shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在看雅各比的节目吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you been watching that show of Jacoby's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,娜丁...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nadine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,去找她吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好与她相守到老吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Enjoy the rest of your lives together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我太开心了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:03.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要一想到你们俩幸福地在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just thinking of you two being happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:06.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德  我爱你  永远都爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed, I love you and always will,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:11.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,但真爱就是要让对方幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but true love is giving the other what makes them happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeez,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这个大块头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you big lug,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,太美好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how beautiful is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,娜丁  我希望你认真思考下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nadine, I want you to think real hard about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说的话  因为你不知道自己在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what you're saying because you're not making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  明天你就会希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Honey, tomorrow, you're gonna wish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:27.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你从没说过这些话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you never said these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德  我说过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed, I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我走了大老远过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I walked all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:35.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有足够的时间思考  反悔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had plenty of time to think, turn back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我真的是这么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because this is how I really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以谢谢安普医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you can thank Dr. Amp,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的老朋友  雅各比医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}our old friend, Dr. Jacoby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说  他大概就是这里唯一一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To me, he's about the only one around here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一说一的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}telling it like it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:51.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, it's just it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:55.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德  你自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed, you are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:58.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,去享受生活吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go and enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:37.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}双R餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:05.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,诺玛  所有事都改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Norma, everything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我刚跟娜丁聊过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just spoke with Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,她给了我自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's given me my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ed, I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔特在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Walter's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你收到我的花了吗  -很美...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Did you get my flowers? - Oh, lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要点什么  艾德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What can I get you, Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,一杯咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,马上送上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,还要一片毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And a cyanide tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要你过来一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I asked you to stop by
