Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.79,0:48:04.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, yeah, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.50,0:48:09.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可真麻烦  查理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're really something, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.98,0:48:11.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.69,0:48:14.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,穿上你的外套  奥黛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put your coat on, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.73,0:48:18.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经很晚了  我很困\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's already late and I'm so sleepy.
